description: The image is a cartoon-style depiction of a young woman dressed as a nun, seemingly in a state of distress. She has blonde, curled hair peeking out from under a white and dark purple habit. Her eyes are wide and blue, and her skin has a pale, almost sickly tone. The woman is holding a red lighter with a bright orange flame in her left hand, while a lit cigarette is held between her red lips. A small mole is visible on her cheek near her mouth. The white collar of her habit is adorned with a small red cross.
